                    <h2 id="endpoints-POSTapi-client-servers-wings--server_uuid--backups--backup_uuid--restore">Handles restoring a backup by making a request to the Wings instance telling it
to begin the process of finding (or downloading) the backup and unpacking it
over the server files.</h2>

<p>
</p>

